{# HyperWeave Stats Frame — Paradigm-dispatched.

   GitHub profile summary card. Paradigm dispatch chooses the layout:

     "brutalist" → brutalist hero-left, 2x2 metric grid, activity bars (495x280)
     "chrome"    → chrome material stack, 4 centered columns, gradient bars (495x260)

   Custom genomes add new paradigms by dropping `frames/stats/{paradigm}-defs.j2`
   and `frames/stats/{paradigm}-content.j2`. Extends document.svg.j2. #}
{% extends "document.svg.j2" %}

{% block defs %}
{% include "frames/stats/" ~ (paradigm | default("brutalist")) ~ "-defs.j2" %}
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
{% include "frames/stats/" ~ (paradigm | default("brutalist")) ~ "-content.j2" %}
{% endblock %}
